            <li>Interested to learn new technologies</li>
        </ul>
        <details>
            <summary>Certificates</summary>
            <ul>
                <li>Director's List - Academic Year 2019/20 Semester 1</li>
                <li>Director's List - Academic Year 2021/22 Semester 2</li>
                <li><a href="https://unity.com/products/unity-certifications/associate-programmer" target="_blank">UCAP-720: Unity Certified Associate: Programmer</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://www.nyp.edu.sg/current-students/academic-matters/nyp-assessment-regulations.html" target="_blank">Director's List</a> - Top 15% in my cohort for the semester
        </details>
        <h1>Contact</h1>
        <p class="social-icon-container">
            <a href="mailto:gnoxnahte.dev@gmail.com" target="_blank"><Image src={EmailIcon} alt="icon" class="social-icon email"></a>
            <a href="https://github.com/GnoxNahte" target="_blank"><Image src={GitHubIcon} alt="icon" class="social-icon"></a>
